 because this discourse by the learned doctor was unlike any that had come from his lips heretofore.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Yes, of course," Faust went on, "I know these things, and many others besides." He chuckled ironically. "I can detect the-harmony of the divine spheres th\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
