, even if she is an old friend, but they tell me it's a Civil Service ruling, only Atropos can do the job, it wouldn't be traditional or within labor regulations to do otherwise! As if tradition and labor regulations were everything!"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Indeed, you have man\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 y problems here," Azzie said. "I feel ashamed of coming to bother you with my own petty concern."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Don't you give it a thought," Lachesis said. "The tea strainer is lovely, and I know just the place for it. Now, what do you have on our mind?"
