riety; or such at least was the assessment of the Heavenly Investigators who checked him out surreptitiously for Michael."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Are you telling me," Azzie said, "that Michael put}{\insrsid6766366 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  }{\insrsid13440386 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Mack up to it? Put the idea in his head of clubbing Faust and going to his house,
