ake some stuff from his house.' Mack then asked, 'But wouldn't that be stealing?' 'In a way,' Babriel replied. 'But if you put ten percent of your receipts in the poorhouse box, the sin will be rescinded.'"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Lachesis admired the tea strainer again, then put\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  it down and said, "That, at least, is the information I have on the matter."
