\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "You've got some growing up to do," Michael said. He hitched his towel more closely about him. "And now may I return to my bath?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Enjoy," Mephistopheles said. "Sorry to have disturbed you."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Michael said to Ylith, "As for you, be\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  good, but not too good, and don't make waves. That's an order."
