 once that it was a Botticelli, one of the middle period of the master's paintings. It was worth a lot of money, and was rather pretty, too.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Surely, Mack thought, in all this great mass of paintings, it wouldn't matter if I took one?
