rom my purpose, which is to take my place in the contest of Dark and Light and so win redemption for mankind and undying glory for myself. Not only that, he gave me a defective Motive Spell, one infected with Jinx, as I see now, which has brought Charon's
\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 boat to a standstill."
