\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 In his sitting room, Dr. Dee, tall and angular, clad in his doctor's gown, was regarding a\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 n ancient volume of curious and forgotten lore. He paused and looked up.
