he Archangel Michael's house was set on an elevated half-acre lot in an exclusive suburb of Heaven. Michael was in the front yard working on his roses. He looked up to see Ylith, the student angel and former witc\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
h, coming up the marble steps.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Ah, there, Ylith, how nice to see you." He put down his trowel and wiped his hands. "Can I get you some lemonade? It's quite a hot day, though dry, a typical heavenly or good sort of day."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "No, thanks," Ylith said. "I came b\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 ecause there's something I'm perplexed about."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Well then," Michael said, "you must tell me all about it. What seems to be the matter?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Ylith said, "I've found evidence that Mephistopheles is cheating."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Aha!" said Michael, but rather mildly. "But that's o\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 nly to be expected, considering who he is."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "What is more disconcerting," Ylith said, "I have also found evidence of }{\cs17\i\insrsid13440386 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 you}{\insrsid13440386 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  cheating."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Me?" Michael said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Yes, you," Ylith said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Michael was silent for a moment, thinking. Then he said, "You are new to our cir\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 cles, aren't you?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Yes, I am," Ylith said. "But what difference\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 "
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Michael held up a hand.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "And therefore you are inexperienced, and lacking in knowledge of the great harmony that holds Good and Bad together in a single unity and dictates the rules of thei\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 r behavior."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "I never even heard of this great harmony," Ylith said. "Does it really make a difference? I'm talking out-and-out cheating."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "All the difference in the world, my dear. For consider: If Light and Dark are to contest at all, they must do so as \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
equals in an ongoing contest, and with the knowledge that to struggle does not mean to win once and for all. Both Good and Bad are interdependent. For the one must exist for there to be the other. Do you understand?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "I think so," Ylith said doubtfully. "B\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 ut what difference\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 "
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
