\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 we know that true victory is neither possible nor practicable, nor even desirable. Are you following?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "I'm not sure," Ylith said. "But please go on."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "It follows that, as equals in the game of Good and Bad, each of us must have access to the same techniqu\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
es. Good must not be handicapped by being forbidden 'bad' alternatives that are available to Dark. Since Bad from time to time uses 'good' means for its own Bad ends, it follows that Good can use 'bad' for its own purposes. The final issue, my dear Ylith,
\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 is not what is good and what is bad, but what is in here." And Michael touched himself in the region of the heart.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Does that mean it's all right for you to cheat?" Ylith asked.
