\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "I hate to contradict you, but you're four hours ate. It's going to make it difficult."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Me? Late? Impossible!" S\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 he turned to Ylith. "What time do you have?"
