 of your clumsy and uninformed efforts to influence history. But despite this being the end, the last word has not yet been spoken. To put it to you succinctly, my dear Mack, Faust himself has not yet been heard from."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Faust? You mean you?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Of course I m\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 ean me! I am Faust, am I not?"
