\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 \hich\f0 "Why\'85\loch\f0  Nothing, I suppose. There's nothing I }{\cs17\i\insrsid13440386 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 can}{\insrsid13440386 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  do. And if there were, why should I?"
