Mephistopheles and the Archangel Michael were sitting side by side on a tall pillar recently vacated by Simon Stylites, who had found a better way to mortify his spirit by picking a punishment from the future and forcing himself to watch t
\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 elevised reruns of every game the Tampa Bay Buccaneers had ever played.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Michael hadn't visited Limbo in quite a while, not since he had met with Mephistopheles to set the contest. He was happy to see that nothing much had changed. There was still the same \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
