\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "You've got a point there," Mephistopheles admitted. "We're both restricted in our viewpoints."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Exactly. That's why we have Ananke to do the judging."
