\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "Really? I didn't know that was the direction to it!"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "It changes from time to time," Michael said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "But why?"
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 "We of the forces of Good," Michael said with dign\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 ity, "try not to spend too much time asking why."
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Mephistopheles shrugged. Together the two great spirits proceeded to the Palace of Justice.
